DataElement.preferredName: Statistics Analysis Plan Document Version Keyword Text ISO21090.DSET.ST.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A representation, conceptually a document, that is created to convey the statistical analysis plan version structured content to human beings. A character string of a word or phrase that describes the document and/or its context. Keywords help users find documents of interest. EXAMPLE(S): species, indication, biocompatibility, drug substance, drug product.
